snippet.title: Best VGM 1533 - Kaiser Knuckle - Wheel of Fortune (Motif of Azteca)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade
Kaiser Knuckle (1994)
Wheel of Fortune (Motif of Azteca)
Yasuhisa Watanabe
